  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p><strong>Race:</strong> Vanara&nbsp;<br /><strong>Replaced Trait(s):</strong> Nimble&nbsp;</p>\n<hr />\n<p>One vanara in every 500 is gifted with limited shapeshifting ability. Such a creature can adjust her size at will. She gains the change shape ability and the shapeshifter subtype. Instead of changing appearance, she can use change shape to reduce her size category to Small. Her ability scores don't change, only her size (and thus her weapon damage); normal size penalties and bonuses to AC and CMD and on attack and skill rolls apply. Changing size or returning to her true size is a fullround action. This racial trait alters the vanara's type and replaces nimble.</p>",
